org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.sharedcachemanager.metrics

Class CleanerMetrics

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.sharedcachemanager.metrics.CleanerMetrics

  • @InterfaceAudience.Private
@InterfaceStability.Evolving
@Metrics(name="CleanerActivity",
         about="Cleaner service metrics",
         context="yarn")
public class CleanerMetrics
extends Object
    This class is for maintaining the various Cleaner activity statistics and publishing them through the metrics interfaces.
